title: GENIE SPACE Medium Vacuum Storage Bags - Pack of 6, 70x50cm | Strong Space Saving Bags | Premium Airtight & Reusable Vacuum Bag for Clothes, Towels, Childrenswear & More | inc Travel Pump
features: INCREASE CLOSET CAPACITY: Ideal for wardrobe and drawer storage, this pack of 6 medium sized suction storage bags are perfect for storing your out of season clothing, such as tops, dresses, cushions, soft toys, children's clothing, etc. The greatest space-saver, these suction compression bags help you create up to 80% more space - perfect for home organisation and travel to make the most out of your space! Includes travel pump.

HEAVY DUTY STRONG: Made using a premium grade double layered material (110 microns thick) for superior strength and reliability, our reusable vacuum bags are airtight, easy to use, and are ideal for long-term use as they will not easily rip, tear or leak air.

100% WATER & AIRTIGHT: With patented anti-leak valve technology and a double ziplock seal, enjoy the peace of mind of your items being protected as these vacuum bags help prevent unwanted odours, moisture, and dust from reaching your stored items - keeping them as fresh and clean as the day they were packed! Suitable for all vacuum types.

UNLOCK MORE SPACE: With incredible compression, air is sucked out of items that have been packed in these vacuum bags to significantly reduce their bulky size by up to 80%, giving you 4 times more space! Essential for moving and perfect for keeping your house and bedroom organised by storing your bags in the wardrobe, closet, loft, garage, or just under the bed!
12 MONTH WARRANTY: We ensure that our products are 100% risk-free with a one-year replacement guarantee. We're only happy if you are!
